# Appendix A: Sample config.ini

```ini
# ergoProtect Configuration File
# Version: 1.0
# All parameters are optional. If omitted, defaults are used.

# Key bindings for mouse actions (F1-F12, A-Z, 0-9 supported)
leftMouseClickKey = F9
rightMouseClickKey = F8
leftMouseDoubleClickKey = F7
leftMouseDragDropKey = F6
activateDeactivateAutoClick = F10

# Auto-click settings
autoClickDelayInMs = 200
autoClickMovementThresholdPx = 3

# Break reminder settings
pauseTimerInMinutes = 40
pauseTimerRestInMinutes = 5
breakCountdownSeconds = 180
breakDelayMinutes = 10

# Logging settings
logMaintainDays = 30
logFilePath = 
logTimezone = local

# Display settings
breakPopupMonitor = primary
```

