# Appendix C: Error Code Reference

| **Error Code** | **Message**                                             | **Severity** | **Action**                                                   |
|----------------|---------------------------------------------------------|--------------|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| E001           | ergoProtect is already running (PID: XXXX)              | ERROR        | Another instance detected. Stop it first or delete stale PID file. |
| E002           | Configuration error: Key 'X' assigned to multiple functions | ERROR    | Fix config.ini to assign unique keys to each function.       |
| E003           | Failed to register keyboard hook: PermissionError       | ERROR        | User lacks permissions. Add to 'input' group (Linux) or run as user (Windows). |
| E004           | logFilePath 'X' not accessible, using executable directory | WARNING   | Check path exists and is writable.                           |
| E005           | Invalid timezone 'X', falling back to 'local'           | WARNING      | Use a valid tz database name or 'local'.                     |
| E006           | Monitor index X exceeds available monitors, using primary | WARNING   | Reduce index or use 'primary'.                               |

